{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e78b47be76","title":"中共中央对安徽省委关于传达、讨论资本主义工商业改造问题的报告的批复","origin":"安徽省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"08fc7f7c45","index":0,"year":1956,"month":2,"day":21,"articleId":"e78b47be76"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"70f97bd032","type":"title","text":"中共中央对安徽省委关于传达、讨论资本主义工商业改造问题的报告的批复","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e78b47be76"},{"id":"f68b5fef87","type":"appellation","text":"安徽省委：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e78b47be76"},{"id":"768a9fe604","type":"paragraph","text":"对你们1月6日关于传达、讨论资本主义工商业改造问题的报告中有关政策性的两个问题，提出以下意见：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e78b47be76"},{"id":"e36239293c","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）长期依靠国家加工订货为生的私营工业，在进行改造的时候，也以先经过公私合营的步骤为妥，不必急于直接改变为社会主义性质的国营加工厂。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e78b47be76"},{"id":"b7472ebe44","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）清产核资中，关于企业多余店（厂）房的处理，原则上均应适当折价、定息。你们所提的“在房屋不缺乏的城市不需折价定息或由其自行处理的办法”恐不妥。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e78b47be76"},{"id":"3b36090d1b","type":"paragraph","text":"其他各项问题，请参阅中央最近所发各项有关的文件。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e78b47be76"},{"id":"66f39de5e4","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央1956年2月21日","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e78b47be76"}],"page":{"id":"f35bebaf7b","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"e78b47be76","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}